svg.text: Will Flags (F=1 or 0) - only present when Will flag is set
Session Expiry Interval (S=F+4 or F) - only present when Sess Exp flag is set
Will Fields (W=4+N+P+S or S) - only present when Will flag is set
Will Topic Alias or Will Topic Name Length MSB
Will Topic Alias or Will Topic Name Length LSB
Will Topic Name (N) - only present when Will Topic Type is Topic Name
Authentication Fields (A=3+M+D+W or W) - only present when Auth flag is set
